# See https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/ignoring-files for more about ignoring files.

# NOTE: /api/ is intentionally NOT gitignored.
# Vercel registers serverless functions from files present in the git clone
# (before the buildCommand runs). api/index.js must exist in the repo so
# Vercel can register it as a function; the buildCommand then overwrites it
# with the fully-bundled Express app.

